data.message: Color accent rules by mood: Single accent discipline creates stronger brand identity. Red #DC2626 = action/energy (CTAs, alerts). Lime #BFFF00 = tech/data/positive metrics. Gold #C9A962 = luxury/premium (use with deep black). Terracotta #C67A52 = organic/sustainable/warm. Coral #FF6B6B = playful/friendly/youthful. Always pair accent with appropriate neutral palette (warm cream for organic, pure black for luxury/tech).
